      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting as a true showroom-quality example. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no visible imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest standards. Buyers can expect a collector-grade car that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
