    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing an outstanding balance of performance and value. This unit exhibits consistent mechanical integrity and has been subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for pre-owned excellence. Featuring a clean profile and a reliable service history, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning buyer seeking quality without compromise.",
